statements: SELECT * FROM influencer_outreach;
SELECT influencer_id, influencer_name FROM influencer_outreach ORDER BY influencer_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM influencer_outreach WHERE response_rate > 0.5;
SELECT influencer_name, email_address, outreach_date FROM influencer_outreach ORDER BY outreach_date ASC;
SELECT influencer_id, response_rate FROM influencer_outreach WHERE influencer_id = 3;
SELECT influencer_name, email_address, response_rate FROM influencer_outreach WHERE outreach_date > '2020-01-01' ORDER BY response_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM influencer_outreach WHERE influencer_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT influencer_name, outreach_date FROM influencer_outreach WHERE response_rate >= 0.5 ORDER BY outreach_date ASC, influencer_name DESC;
SELECT email_address FROM influencer_outreach WHERE response_rate < 0.2 AND outreach_date BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-12-31';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_outreach, AVG(response_rate) AS avg_response_rate FROM influencer_outreach WHERE response_rate IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM influencers;
SELECT id, name, followers_count FROM influencers ORDER BY followers_count DESC;
SELECT name, email, engagement_rate FROM influencers WHERE engagement_rate > 5;
SELECT influencer_id, email_subject, response_rate, response_status FROM outreach_data WHERE response_rate >= 0.5;
SELECT id, name, email, followers_count, engagement_rate FROM influencers WHERE followers_count < 1000;
SELECT * FROM influencers WHERE followers_count > 1000 ORDER BY engagement_rate DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT name, email, followers_count FROM influencers WHERE followers_count BETWEEN 500 AND 2000 ORDER BY followers_count ASC
SELECT id, email_date, email_subject FROM outreach_data WHERE influencer_id = 5 ORDER BY email_date DESC

SELECT * FROM influencers JOIN outreach_data ON influencers.id = outreach_data.influencer_id WHERE influencers.followers_count > 5000 AND outreach_data.response_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY influencers.followers_count DESC, outreach_data.response_rate DESC
SELECT * FROM influencers WHERE name LIKE '%influencer%' AND (followers_count > 2000 OR engagement_rate < 2.0) ORDER BY engagement_rate ASC,followers_count DESC

SELECT name, email FROM Influencers WHERE followers > 10000;

SELECT influencers.name, emailcommunications.subject, responserates.response_rate FROM Influencers JOIN EmailCommunications ON influencers.id = emailcommunications.influencer_id JOIN ResponseRates ON emailcommunications.id = responserates.communication_id WHERE influencers.followers > 5000;

SELECT name, followers FROM Influencers ORDER BY followers DESC;

SELECT Influencers.name, EmailCommunications.subject FROM Influencers INNER JOIN EmailCommunications ON Influencers.id = EmailCommunications.influencer_id;

SELECT Influencers.name, EmailCommunications.subject, ResponseRates.response_rate FROM Influencers JOIN EmailCommunications ON Influencers.id = EmailCommunications.influencer_id JOIN ResponseRates ON EmailCommunications.id = ResponseRates.communication_id WHERE ResponseRates.response_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY ResponseRates.response_rate DESC;

SELECT * FROM influencer_outreach;
SELECT email_address, communication_date FROM influencer_outreach ORDER BY communication_date DESC;
SELECT content_id, content_title, content_type FROM outreach_content WHERE influencer_id = 'abc123';
SELECT email_subject, email_date FROM emails WHERE influencer_id = 'xyz789' AND email_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT influencer_id, response_date, response_rating FROM response_rates WHERE response_rating >= 4.5 ORDER BY response_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM influencer_outreach WHERE response_rate > 50;
SELECT email_address, communication_date FROM influencer_outreach WHERE influencer_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT c.content_title, c.content_type, o.email_subject FROM outreach_content c JOIN emails o ON c.influencer_id = o.influencer_id WHERE c.content_type = 'Blog Post' AND o.email_date >= '2022-01-01';

SELECT r.response_date, r.response_rating, op.outreach_success FROM response_rates r JOIN outreach_performance op ON r.influencer_id = op.influencer_id WHERE r.response_rating < 4.0 AND op.outreach_success = TRUE;
SELECT DISTINCT io.email_address, e.email_subject FROM influencer_outreach io LEFT JOIN emails e ON io.influencer_id = e.influencer_id;
